SQL: select count(*) from cis_case cc inner join case_prty_role cpr on cpr.case_id = cc.case_identifier inner join role_typ_cd rtc on cpr.role_typ_cd = rtc.role_type_code_identifier inner join pers p on p.prty_id = cpr.prty_id inner join pers_race pr on pr.prty_id = p.prty_id inner join race_cd race on race.race_cd_id = pr.race_cd_id where cc.uscis_receipt_number='${USCIS Receipt Number}' and rtc.role_type_description = 'Applicant' and race.race_cd_id = (SELECT COALESCE((select race_cd_id from race_cd where race_lckbx_cd='${Applicant Race 2}'), -1) FROM DUAL)

select count(*) from cis_case cc inner join case_prty_role cpr on cpr.case_id = cc.case_identifier inner join role_typ_cd rtc on cpr.role_typ_cd = rtc.role_type_code_identifier inner join pers p on p.prty_id = cpr.prty_id inner join eye_color_cd eye on eye.eye_color_cd_id = p.eye_color_cd inner join hair_color_cd hc on hc.hair_color_cd_id = p.hair_color_cd where cc.uscis_receipt_number='${USCIS Receipt Number}' and rtc.role_type_description = 'Applicant' and eye.eye_color_cd_id = (SELECT COALESCE((select eye_color_cd_id from eye_color_cd where eye_color_lckbx_cd='${Applicant Eye Color}'), -1) FROM DUAL) and hc.hair_color_cd_id = (SELECT COALESCE((select hair_color_cd_id from hair_color_cd where hair_color_lckbx_cd='${Applicant Hair Color}'), -1) FROM DUAL) and p.ethnicity_cd IS NULL and p.hgt_inchs_meas = (SELECT COALESCE(NULLIF('${Applicant Height}',''), '0') FROM DUAL) and p.wgt_lbs_wgt = (SELECT COALESCE(NULLIF('${Applicant Weight}',''), '0') FROM DUAL)

select count(*) from cis_case cc inner join case_prty_role cpr on cpr.case_id = cc.case_identifier inner join role_typ_cd rtc on cpr.role_typ_cd = rtc.role_type_code_identifier inner join pers p on p.prty_id = cpr.prty_id inner join eye_color_cd eye on eye.eye_color_cd_id = p.eye_color_cd inner join hair_color_cd hc on hc.hair_color_cd_id = p.hair_color_cd where cc.uscis_receipt_number='${USCIS Receipt Number}' and rtc.role_type_description = 'Applicant' and eye.eye_color_cd_id = (SELECT COALESCE((select eye_color_cd_id from eye_color_cd where eye_color_lckbx_cd='${Applicant Eye Color}'), -1) FROM DUAL) and hc.hair_color_cd_id = (SELECT COALESCE((select hair_color_cd_id from hair_color_cd where hair_color_lckbx_cd='${Applicant Hair Color}'), -1) FROM DUAL) and p.ethnicity_cd = (select ethnic_cd_id from ethnicity_cd where ethnic_alt_cd='${Applicant Ethnicity}') and p.hgt_inchs_meas = (SELECT COALESCE(NULLIF('${Applicant Height}',''), '0') FROM DUAL) and p.wgt_lbs_wgt = (SELECT COALESCE(NULLIF('${Applicant Weight}',''), '0') FROM DUAL)

select count(*) from cis_case cc inner join case_prty_role cpr on cpr.case_id = cc.case_identifier inner join role_typ_cd rtc on cpr.role_typ_cd = rtc.role_type_code_identifier inner join pers p on p.prty_id = cpr.prty_id inner join aln_nbr an on an.prty_id = cpr.prty_id where cc.uscis_receipt_number='${USCIS Receipt Number}' and rtc.role_type_description = 'Applicant' and an.aln_nbr_prim_ind = 'Y' and an.delete_ind = 'N' and an.aln_nbr = '${Applicant Alien Number}'

Precondition: '${Applicant State Of Birth}' != '' || '${Applicant Place Of Birth}' != ''
Test: Verify Applicant Birth Location for I821D and 765
Result: 1,${Applicant Place Of Birth}, ${Applicant State Of Birth}
SQL: select count(*), p.brth_plce_desc from cis_case cc inner join case_prty_role cpr on cpr.case_id = cc.case_identifier inner join role_typ_cd rtc on cpr.role_typ_cd = rtc.role_type_code_identifier inner join pers p on p.prty_id = cpr.prty_id where cc.uscis_receipt_number='${USCIS Receipt Number}' and rtc.role_type_description = 'Applicant' and p.brth_cntry_cd = (SELECT COALESCE((select brth_cntry_cd from brth_cntry_cd where lckbx_cntry_cd='${Applicant Country Of Birth}'), 'UNKNO') FROM DUAL)  group by p.brth_plce_desc
